COLGATE-PALMOLIVE Co. (New York) -- Craig B. Tate was named to the new post of vice president, global business development, at this household and personal products company.
He had been vice president, world-wide marketing.
James Figura was named vice president, consumer research and insights, expanding his previous duties as director of marketing research.
David A. Metzler was named president of the Colgate Latin America division, a new post.
He had been vice president in charge of the division.
Alois D. Juliber was named to the new post of president of the Colgate Far East and Canada divisions.
She had been vice president of the Far East division. 

